article.description: — Jao Ituka had 25 points as Marist easily defeated Monmouth 83-58 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Ituka lifts Marist over Monmouth 83-58
article.story: WEST LONG BRANCH, N.J. -- — Jao Ituka had 25 points as Marist easily defeated Monmouth 83-58 on Tuesday night. Ricardo Wright added 20 points for Marist (9-13, 4-9 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference), which ended its five-game losing streak. Noah Harris had 13 points. Matt Herasme added six rebounds. Walker Miller had 17 points and eight rebounds for the Hawks (15-8, 7-5). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
